       E - Services:


         Below are Services that you can access and interact with online.

      Residential Parcel Info and Comps


      Search for residential parcel inforamtion by parcel number or
   name/street. You can then view Comparables (COMPS) and see Tax Bill
                              information.

      Justice Courts Schedule


   Get the current daily schedules of all of the Justice Courts in
                          Maricopa County.

      Interactive Maps of Maricopa County


    Use this interactive map to find a wealth of information such as;
   parcel and zoning data, fire and police stations locations, aerial
   photos, and much more. Presented by the Assessor G.I.S. Division.

      Public Access to Court Information


   From here you can obtain Case History information by name or case
      number and Court Calendar information by department / date.

      Jobs at Maricopa County


   Find all current job openings at Maricopa County and download
                      application materials.

      Recorded Documents from the County Recorder


   Plat maps, deeds, titles, etc. are all available online with many
                       different ways to search.

      Restaurant Ratings


     Search for restaurants by name to see how they have scored on their
   current and past health inspections with detailed descriptions of each
                                 violation.

      Self-Service Center of the Superior Court of Arizona in Maricopa County


   Find Court information, Forms / Instructions, and Lawyers & Mediators.

      Property Tax Statement


   Get your current Property Tax Statement online by entering your parcel
                                  number.

      Adoptable Pets


   Find a pet online! Use this service to find a dog or cat that needs a
                                   home.



   Site Map     What's New

